              <li><span>Fred Wilson </span>just signed up!</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="email-content">
              <li>His twitter account is <a href="#">@fredwilson</a> and he has <span>450,000</span> followers.</li>
              <li>He is a developer. His GitHub account is <a href="#">@fwilson</a>.</li>
              <li>He works for a recently funded startup.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row" style="margin: 60px 0">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 20px 0">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">
          <div class="media">
            <div class="media-left">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 50px">1.</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="media-body">
              <h4 style="margin: 0">You install our script</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
